Package: ggAtlasTrack
Title: ggplot2 Visualisation Tools for AtlasTrack White Matter Tracts
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hollie", "Byrne", , "hollie.byrne@sydney.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides ggplot2-based two-dimensional visualisations of AtlasTrack white-matter tract polygons in three view sets - orthogonal, ggseg, and axial. Supports categorical tract plots and tract-level continuous values.
